          <title>
            <string language="en">Transpiration lab</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Transpirationlabor</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Laboratoire de transpiration</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Laboratório do transpiration</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Laboratorio della traspirazione</string>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Εργαστήριο εφίδρωσης</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Laboratorio de la transpiración</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">In this activity, your students will observe the process of transpiration. They will determine the rate of transpiration for one plant branch.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
            <string language="en">Science and Technology</string>
          </keyword>
          <language>en</language>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">In dieser Aktivität beobachten Ihre 
Kursteilnehmer den Prozeß von Transpiration. Sie stellen die 
Kinetik von Transpiration für einen Betriebszweig fest.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Dans cette activité, vos étudiants observeront 
le processus de la transpiration. Ils détermineront la cadence 
de la transpiration pour un branchement d'usine.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Nesta atividade, seus estudantes observarão o 
processo do transpiration. Determinarão a taxa do transpiration
para uma filial da planta.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">In questa attività, i vostri allievi osserveranno
il processo della traspirazione. Determineranno il tasso della 
traspirazione per un ramo della pianta.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Σε αυτήν την δραστηριότητα, οι σπουδαστές σας θα 
παρατηρήσουν τη διαδικασία της εφίδρωσης. Θα καθορίσουν το 
ποσοστό εφίδρωσης για έναν κλάδο εγκαταστάσεων.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">En esta actividad, sus estudiantes observarán el 
proceso de la transpiración. Determinarán el índice de la 
transpiración para una ramificación de la planta.</string>
          </description>
          <keyword>
